Dad, look, many trees.

78
00:04:10,273 --> 00:04:12,673
That tree's big!

79
00:04:12,709 --> 00:04:14,472
Already gone.

80
00:04:15,245 --> 00:04:16,712
Come on.

81
00:04:16,780 --> 00:04:18,372
Can l concede the loss?

82
