1022
00:47:17,257 --> 00:47:18,315
Tso.

1023
00:47:20,160 --> 00:47:21,821
You're responsible.

1024
00:47:22,196 --> 00:47:23,925
Well,

1025
00:47:23,964 --> 00:47:26,364
